message.content: Based on the available information, it is not possible to provide an accurate summary of what most women in Grenada think of divorce. Public opinion on divorce can vary greatly depending on individuals' personal and cultural beliefs, values, and experiences. Additionally, attitudes towards divorce might have shifted over time as societal norms change. To accurately understand the opinions of women in Grenada regarding divorce, it would be necessary to conduct a comprehensive study or survey dedicated to this topic.
